"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-football-romero-olympics-2024-tottenham-argentina-postecoglou-b1148505.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Football  Your matchday briefing on Tottenham, featuring team news and expert analysis from Sam Tabuteau    I would like to be emailed about offers, event and updates from Evening Standard.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 271, \"end\": 280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tottenham_Hotspur_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999627107, \"rank\": 3.741341593697667e-11, \"text\": \"Tottenham\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tottenham_Hotspur_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tottenham_Hotspur_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 327, \"end\": 330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9979562495775373, \"rank\": 0.0008873095700799146, \"text\": \"Sam\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 331, \"end\": 339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Tabuteau\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tabuteau\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Tabuteau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Tabuteau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tottenhamhead coachAnge Postecoglousays the club could blockCristian Romerofrom playing forArgentinaat theOlympicsand will \\\"strongly\\\" advise the defender to rest instead.\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Romero hassaid he would \\\"love\\\" to be one of his country's three over-23 picksfor the tournament at the Paris Games, which runs from July 24 to August 10 -- finishing just a week before the start of the new Premier League season.\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 622, \"end\": 628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_A._Romero\", \"score\": 0.999992890394686, \"rank\": 7.070843303086005e-06, \"text\": \"Romero\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_A._Romero\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_A._Romero\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Spurs vice-captain is already certain to be included in Argentina's squad for the Copa America, starting in mid-June and concluding on July 15, and Postecoglou wants Romero to be fresh for the \\\"big season\\\" ahead.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 1068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 912, \"end\": 921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999881506704737, \"rank\": 0.00011842030204392513, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1022, \"end\": 1028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_A._Romero\", \"score\": 0.999992890394686, \"rank\": 7.070843303086005e-06, \"text\": \"Romero\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_A._Romero\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_A._Romero\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Olympics is a little bit of a different issue because club's are not obliged to let players go to the Olympics,\\\" Postecoglou said.\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From that perspective, we have a little bit more of a say in it than other internationals.\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Certainly from our behalf as a club, we will always be looking at making sure there is a balance there.\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He has not spoken to me about it, no one has spoken to me about it but I guess pretty strong advice would be with the Copa America at the same time and hopefully us gearing up for a big season next year, I'd be suggesting rest is a better policy.\\\"\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1648, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tottenham vs Luton: Prediction, kick-off time, TV, live stream, team news, h2h results, odds  Micky van de Ven offers Tottenham a major boost as defender available for Luton clash  Tottenham: No need for Ange Postecoglou panic... just look at Mikel Arteta and Jurgen Klopp examples  Tottenham'scontroversial plans for a post-season friendly against Newcastle in Melbourneon May 22, three days after the end of the campaign, have already increased the demands on their internationals ahead of the summer tournaments.\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tottenham_Hotspur_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999627107, \"rank\": 3.741341593697667e-11, \"text\": \"Tottenham\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tottenham_Hotspur_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tottenham_Hotspur_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1818, \"end\": 1823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luton_Town_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999974597354118, \"rank\": 2.540262088481035e-06, \"text\": \"Luton\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luton_Town_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luton_Town_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1831, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tottenham_Hotspur_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999627107, \"rank\": 3.741341593697667e-11, \"text\": \"Tottenham\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tottenham_Hotspur_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tottenham_Hotspur_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1854, \"end\": 1870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ange_Postecoglou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ange Postecoglou\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ange_Postecoglou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ange_Postecoglou\"}, {\"begin\": 1910, \"end\": 1922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J\\u00fcrgen_Klopp\", \"score\": 0.9999999976453182, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jurgen Klopp\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J\\u00fcrgen_Klopp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J\\u00fcrgen_Klopp\"}, {\"begin\": 1999, \"end\": 2008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_United_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.927280670578563e-19, \"text\": \"Newcastle\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_United_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_United_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Postecoglou says he was involved in the decision to visit his hometown and insists the club carefully weighed up the pros and cons.\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I guess with all these decisions there is always going to be conjecture and scrutiny around why they are made,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But from our perspective, like any club, you weigh up the benefits and costs of doing something.\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For one reason or another, we have not had a lot of games this year and there was a unique opportunity for us to have a game at the end of the year.\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2669, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am obviously part of that discussion and we are mindful of the players and the schedule.\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2762, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We weighed it all up and thought it was going to be really beneficial for us as a football club, and we have gone that way.\\\"\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Spurs return to action with a visit from Luton Town on Saturday and Postecoglou expects the struggling Hatters to have a go at his side, who are aiming to bounce back from achastening 3-0 defeat at Fulhambefore the international break.\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 3124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You hear a lot of coaches say they are going to go all-out attack but Rob [Edwards, Luton boss] backs up his words with action,\\\" Postecoglou said.\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3211, \"end\": 3216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luton_Town_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999974597354118, \"rank\": 2.540262088481035e-06, \"text\": \"Luton\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luton_Town_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luton_Town_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I have seen them play against City or Liverpool or Arsenal, any of the top clubs, they have still gone out and been really aggressive.\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3319, \"end\": 3328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0275446646555617e-20, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 3332, \"end\": 3339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arsenal_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 1.2264121547294311e-11, \"text\": \"Arsenal\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arsenal_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arsenal_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are going to be really aggressive against us and we have got to be ready for it.\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I said after the [Fulham] game we did not work as hard as we had been in other games.\", \"from\": 3503, \"to\": 3589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3522, \"end\": 3528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.646475150603926e-17, \"text\": \"Fulham\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was probably the first game this year where I felt our competitive level were not where they should have been and when they are not, you will pay a price.\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We did on the day and I thought Fulham were good.\", \"from\": 3750, \"to\": 3799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3782, \"end\": 3788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.646475150603926e-17, \"text\": \"Fulham\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We addressed it with the guys and we will have to get back up to where we have been for a tough game tomorrow.\\\"\", \"from\": 3801, \"to\": 3913, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 4793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3975, \"end\": 3984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\", \"score\": 0.7144681023415381, \"rank\": 0.39832297251777016, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\"}, {\"begin\": 4075, \"end\": 4084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\", \"score\": 0.7144681023415381, \"rank\": 0.39832297251777016, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\"}, {\"begin\": 4153, \"end\": 4161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource